# Personal hum harvester overlay drop.
#
# Files placed here (e.g. `exercise.mjs`, `dining.mjs`, `stocks.mjs`) are
# discovered by `agent/scripts/hum-harvest-all.mjs` at run time and
# registered identically to the bundled harvesters in the parent dir.
#
# Naming: `<topic>.mjs` where <topic> matches the `name` field in your
# `data/hum-interests.json`. The bundled harvesters take precedence; the
# loader only looks here for topics not satisfied by the kernel set.
#
# Anything you place under `_ext/` is gitignored — see .gitignore at repo
# root and docs/architecture-public-private.md.
